Class DefaultFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.DefaultFactory

  • public class DefaultFactory
extends Object
    A factory for creating default objects. Has a Configuration object from where it retrieves the default settings from.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      DefaultFactory()
      With no passed in parameters the default factory uses a new Configuration object.
      DefaultFactory(Configuration configuration)
      Initializes the factory with existing configuration.
